Package: UCell
Type: Package
Title: Robust single-cell signature enrichment analysis for Seurat
Version: 1.3.1
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = 'Massimo', family = 'Andreatta', email = 'massimo.andreatta@unil.ch', role = c('aut','cre'), comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0002-8036-2647')),
  person(given = 'Santiago', family = 'Carmona', email = 'santiago.carmona@unil.ch', role = c('aut'), comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0002-2495-0671'))
  )
Description: UCell extends Seurat package functionalities to calculate gene module/signature enrichment scores in single-cell transcriptomes using the Mann-Whitney U statistic. The normalized U statistic is mathematically related to the area under the ROC curve and it depends only on the gene expression ranks of each cell. 
Depends: R(>= 3.6.1) 
Imports: data.table(>= 1.13.6), 
         Matrix, 
         future,
         future.apply,
         SingleCellExperiment
Suggests: Seurat
